We chose GPT-4o-mini [openai2024gpt4technicalreport] for our experiments, because of (i) its ability to process requests in batches, (ii) its structured output feature, (iii) its good tradeoff between performance and cost. The batch feature is particularly important, enabling us to send, after startup, up to 100 batches of 10,000 entities in parallel. The model's size is not publicly released, but has been estimated to be around 8B [gptparameters1,gptparameters2].